reviews.review_text: Had a great experience at the photo lab of London Drugs today. I didnt catch the gentlemans name, but he was working on Saturday July 29th at 2:25pm, he said he was off at 5:30pm. There is another popular photography studio down the street that does passport photos beside a denture and tax business. But they were so busy they couldnt give me a time to come back. Plus their cost was a bit higher. So I decided to go to London Drugs as my face was already done with full on makeup...I didnt want to redo my look or come back at another time. The gentleman that took my pic was super patient and kind, I didnt feel rushed and he let me retake a few to see which picture I prefered. The camera had a flash mount attached to it, so your face looks flawless, no filter needed :P He was non-judgemental and super fast in developing the pics as well. 2 hard copies with taxes came to $17.91! Plus all sorts of payments are accepted at LD :) The pictures are enclosed in an envelope and stamped at the back. If you need a digital copy, its $4. But you dont really need digital copies for a Canadian passport renewal. Highly recommended to come here!!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hello Lori! We are so happy to hear that we were able to assist you with your passport.  Thank you for letting us know and for taking the time to write this 5-star review We hope to see you soon. Regards, Mike
